String.string: You fool! You led them to me.
Forgive me, mistress!
Show yourself!
Can't be! How could they know...?
Their presence is an inconvenience I could do without.
Now, for your penance...
Please, mistress, no. Please!
Silence! Obey my will!
Aaah... Aarrrgh!
Look, Zolyn! It's bigger on the inside!
Oh. Okay.
Oh, don't worry. I am fine.
It can't be true! All of these monsters were... people?
Get out of my way!
Curse these archdevas!
Rhodos, I know you're shocked, but we have to catch her.
You are right. What she did, though...
This isn't the time for grief. Let's move!
That witch! She magicked him into a demokron!
We must stop the archdevas.
Oh, wait! Don't go alone, Zolyn!
